		+ generate correct unsigned defines (Michael)
		+ handle NULL obj / impl cleanly (Mark)

	* Misc.
		+ more regression tests (Mark)
		+ autoconf updates (Sam Couter)
		+ IOP profile fixage (Roland Juelich, Marl)
		+ spec fixage (Ross Golder)

